              "img_source": "SOE Picture Dictionary \u2014 Land 5",
              "phonetic": "RUN | JUMP | SWIM | KICK | THROW",
              "instructions": "Do each action for 10 seconds: hop on one foot, march in place, jump with both feet, spin slowly. Rest and breathe.",
              "tip": "Nerissa says: Every time you move, you make your heart stronger. Go team!"
