              "img_source": "SOE Picture Dictionary \u2014 Land 4",
              "phonetic": "oh-SHUN | FISH | KOR-ul | WAIV | DEAP",
              "instructions": "Find 3 ocean creatures in the picture. Draw your favorite in the box below. Write its name and one amazing fact about it.",
